{"tid":21572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得,毒係一種心境?","createTime":"2016-12-04T02:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T07:40:33.000Z","uid":41552,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f38bb6496ec0da24c0ea6979e0721ac227d16b31","tid":21572,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"睇到熱門到嗰義工post<br />\n有感而發<br />\n<br />\n其實毒係一種心境<br />\n一種mental state<br />\n係一種鍾意自己獨處嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n但鍾意自己毒 <br />\n唔等同唔識 唔可以同人social 有社交活動 <br />\n而係你有咁嘅能力 但你唔太好咁做 <br />\n而唔係你無咁嘅能力 所以唔可以咁做 <br />\n兩者係有分別嘅<br />\n<br />\n大佬<br />\n見到人唔出聲唔盛就跟人嗰啲唔係叫毒 <br />\n係連基本嘅社交能力都缺乏左 <br />\n<br />\n毒 唔係無社交能力 <br />\n係有能力但唔鍾意咁做 <br />\n<br />\n啲人講嘅偽毒 <br />\n其實係另外一樣嘢 <br />\n只係啲本身MK嘅包裝自己嘅一種手法<br />\n<br />\n毒究竟係啲咩,唔知大家又點睇"},{"pid":"ff3bc7b7ce9c40f48937f243fc8a25601f453fc0","tid":21572,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94e40623dd01c0f9ff3a54d5ed9af56af142a7fc","tid":21572,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"樓上做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3cecbcb327d01091307ee68c8338beee1d23a2","tid":21572,"uid":51573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:17:07.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒係一種境界<br />\n申利：平時好撚sociable 日日出街但其實內心好撚毒一得閒就會推晒d 約自閉屈屋企幾日唔出街"},{"pid":"f7e7a84db664b18e2e2168a43dfafa2b92d71081","tid":21572,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒係一種境界<br />\n申利：平時好撚sociable 日日出街但其實內心好撚毒一得閒就會推晒d 約自閉屈屋企幾日唔出街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係而家毒嗰定義好似已經俾人扭曲左<br />\n好似毒係解無社交能力咁"},{"pid":"20e40eb0b6602e86f56c5cc264483046102fbe28","tid":21572,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"善於社交的毒撚"},{"pid":"24015221952c5a6bf1fd62ccbc6e4c5d5def47d4","tid":21572,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:20:49.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算係<br />\n本身係sales<br />\n一番工就鬼上身咁把口收唔到係咁挖話題傾<br />\n一收工唔好話電話或一般對話，就連whatsapp都唔想睇<br />\n番到屋企部電話多數set震機<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99637882bb77179f1da3bb17f027c969b29bff96","tid":21572,"uid":51573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒係一種境界<br />\n申利：平時好撚sociable 日日出街但其實內心好撚毒一得閒就會推晒d 約自閉屈屋企幾日唔出街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係而家毒嗰定義好似已經俾人扭曲左<br />\n好似毒係解無社交能力咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家d 人腦退化多<br />\n唔識有好多面示人<br />\n其實一個人有好多面唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff011ead22eefd22e1dae20a36735eb7b7d71a82","tid":21572,"uid":53972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:23:02.000Z","msg":"好認同<br />\n利申：鐘意獨處，成日畀人約都係推得就推"},{"pid":"4ebc848dd991be0711c1fadf8667e82729bc7986","tid":21572,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>善於社交的毒撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你無講錯<br />\n<br />\n唔通人唔可以叻做嗰樣嘢但唔鍾意做嗰樣嘢咩<br />\n大把啦"},{"pid":"9b336f27becb7f0eaaec10b41c8b584c0f182625","tid":21572,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒係一種境界<br />\n申利：平時好撚sociable 日日出街但其實內心好撚毒一得閒就會推晒d 約自閉屈屋企幾日唔出街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係而家毒嗰定義好似已經俾人扭曲左<br />\n好似毒係解無社交能力咁&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家d 人腦退化多<br />\n唔識有好多面示人<br />\n其實一個人有好多面唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解<br />\n講到好似一定係好linear咁<br />\n<br />\n大佬<br />\n正路應該都識睇唔同場合俾唔同反應啦"},{"pid":"ad1ea72c383af5c1edcab1df9cda0cc5960b8b6b","tid":21572,"uid":5990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:27:32.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩開班Friend成日話我僞毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對公眾講野唔會口窒窒 又敢主動撩新朋友講野<br />\n但其實我係好憎同人溝通交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以前因為唔想同人wts成日hea覆已讀人地 而家個wts十年都唔響一次 我樂得清閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願自己一個獨處都唔會浪費時間係其他無聊人身上<br />\n偽毒 係MK扮毒撚<br />\n毒的境界 係吾不能變心而從俗兮 固將愁苦而終窮的抱負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世人話我成日孤身隻影好可憐 我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5435f0c0269261cf5ba47d005263aef3d35006a0","tid":21572,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒係一種境界<br />\n申利：平時好撚sociable 日日出街但其實內心好撚毒一得閒就會推晒d 約自閉屈屋企幾日唔出街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係而家毒嗰定義好似已經俾人扭曲左<br />\n好似毒係解無社交能力咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家d 人腦退化多<br />\n唔識有好多面示人<br />\n其實一個人有好多面唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7a78672c62ea5d61fa3e30226375bdd261e469","tid":21572,"uid":51573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"有時sociable 都係工作需要生活需要姐<br />\n有呢個技巧唔代表我好撚鐘意應酬你班低能仔架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45579e17a0ec2eab046fde320778532cad679cf5","tid":21572,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時sociable 都係工作需要生活需要姐<br />\n有呢個技巧唔代表我好撚鐘意應酬你班低能仔架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但而家啲人覺得好似唔識應酬先係毒<br />\n<br />\n其實係正視聽<br />\n點解啲人會誤解左毒個本意<br />\n咪就係因爲有好似狗公坤嗰啲真mk話自己毒囉 <br />\n嗰啲就叫偽毒啦<br />\n<br />\n其實嗰重點係在於<br />\n自己好唔好嗰樣嘢<br />\n識social但其實鍾意獨處嘅 <br />\n咪係心境毒囉"},{"pid":"69d34f26a687ffb919ece9440180efa206a7c50c","tid":21572,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩開班Friend成日話我僞毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對公眾講野唔會口窒窒 又敢主動撩新朋友講野<br />\n但其實我係好憎同人溝通交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以前因為唔想同人wts成日hea覆已讀人地 而家個wts十年都唔響一次 我樂得清閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願自己一個獨處都唔會浪費時間係其他無聊人身上<br />\n偽毒 係MK扮毒撚<br />\n毒的境界 係吾不能變心而從俗兮 固將愁苦而終窮的抱負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世人話我成日孤身隻影好可憐 我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打嘅&ldquo;吾不能變心而從俗兮&rdquo;已經係最高境界<br />\n可以唔理其他人<br />\n真真正正enjoy自己一個毒"},{"pid":"e997e018d7a5958184add7f33bba5e927aec4161","tid":21572,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"